7. session survives app restart;
8. session survives device reboot;
9. browser refresh survives;
10. Render restart does not break access;
11. logout invalidates session;
12. revoked session returns 401;
13. denied permission returns 403;
14. no Expo Go owner-proof gate;
15. no duplicate login store;
16. no false blocked banner.

